6
00:00:15,600 --> 00:00:17,000
What about the son
of Professor Ren, Tian Zhen?

7
00:00:17,240 --> 00:00:18,520
He studied TCM since young.

8
00:00:18,760 --> 00:00:20,360
Diagnosing minor illnesses as such

9
00:00:20,360 --> 00:00:21,600
is second nature to him.

10
00:00:21,600 --> 00:00:22,400
And, he's good at

11
00:00:22,400 --> 00:00:24,280
both TCM Acupuncture

12
00:00:24,400 --> 00:00:25,760
and brewing medicine.

13
00:00:26,040 --> 00:00:27,640
Mr Zheng, you don't
need to worry at all.

14
00:00:31,440 --> 00:00:32,320
Mr Ren,

15
00:00:32,360 --> 00:00:33,160
I'm a paediatrician.

16
00:00:33,160 --> 00:00:33,960
I should go.

17
00:00:34,440 --> 00:00:35,800
This is the territory of
TCM practitioners.

18
00:00:35,800 --> 00:00:36,800
You can stay here.

19
00:00:37,120 --> 00:00:38,280
But when it comes to sick children...

20
00:00:44,080 --> 00:00:45,640
Mr Ren, I'll go.

21
00:00:47,240 --> 00:00:48,040
Li Quan will do.

22
00:00:48,160 --> 00:00:49,520
He and Tian Zhen are classmates.

23
00:00:49,680 --> 00:00:51,160
Both of them are
Professor Ren's students.

24
00:00:51,320 --> 00:00:52,840
We can assess their result.

25
00:00:53,400 --> 00:00:54,200
Yes.

26
00:00:54,400 --> 00:00:56,000
Professor Ren, Mr Wu,

27
00:00:56,040 --> 00:00:57,440
I do acknowledge

28
00:00:57,440 --> 00:00:58,760
their academic qualifications.

29
00:00:59,640 --> 00:01:01,480
However, I was only given
this daughter in my old age.

30
00:01:02,400 --> 00:01:03,680
She was spoiled since young.

31
00:01:03,680 --> 00:01:05,400
Her body is weak.

32
00:01:05,400 --> 00:01:07,160
Having a fever might be a minor illness.

33
00:01:07,160 --> 00:01:08,360
But she contracted pneumonia

34
00:01:08,360 --> 00:01:09,400
and got a hormone shot

35
00:01:09,400 --> 00:01:10,480
for a fever last year.

36
00:01:10,480 --> 00:01:12,240
Although it didn't develop into asthma,

37
00:01:12,240 --> 00:01:13,080
she still

38
00:01:13,080 --> 00:01:15,000
wheezes from time to time.

39
00:01:15,400 --> 00:01:17,080
Professor Ren,

40
00:01:17,160 --> 00:01:17,960
please give her a diagnosis.

41
00:01:17,960 --> 00:01:19,240
Look at how anxious he is.

42
00:01:20,480 --> 00:01:21,320
You see.

43
00:01:21,880 --> 00:01:23,600
