when she starts crying.

70
00:02:33,720 --> 00:02:34,520
Can she take medicinal brew then?

71
00:02:35,640 --> 00:02:36,760
No.

72
00:02:37,080 --> 00:02:38,640
We let her try it when she was little.

73
00:02:38,640 --> 00:02:39,760
She couldn't take it.

74
00:02:40,160 --> 00:02:41,840
There's no need for
any medicine or needles.

75
00:02:46,080 --> 00:02:47,240
Where's your kitchen?

76
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:48,840
Kitchen?

77
00:03:00,240 --> 00:03:01,160
You put that much?

78
00:03:41,200 --> 00:03:41,920
Done.

79
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:42,840
This is it?

80
00:03:44,080 --> 00:03:44,960
Kitchen cures everything.

81
00:03:44,960 --> 00:03:45,800
Take it to her.

82
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:46,640
Tell her to take it while it's hot.

83
00:04:12,920 --> 00:04:14,040
Tou Tou, what are you doing?

84
00:04:15,200 --> 00:04:16,240
I'm making egg yolk oil.

85
00:04:16,520 --> 00:04:17,920
Egg yolk oil doesn't cure
the common cold.

86
00:04:18,080 --> 00:04:19,000
I know.

87
00:04:21,320 --> 00:04:22,360
Stop messing around.

88
00:04:22,360 --> 00:04:23,200
I'm not.

89
00:04:23,200 --> 00:04:24,440
Wait outside.

90
00:04:28,760 --> 00:04:29,640
Done.

91
00:04:35,520 --> 00:04:36,400
You're done?

92
00:04:37,720 --> 00:04:38,600
Let's go.

93
00:04:44,880 --> 00:04:45,920
She finished the soup, right?

94
00:04:46,920 --> 00:04:48,000
Yes, but...

95
00:04:51,040 --> 00:04:52,000
What do you mean?

96
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:52,800
What happened after that?

97
00:04:53,640 --> 00:04:54,440
Tang Tang said

98
00:04:54,440 --> 00:04:55,880
it tasted like instant noodles'
soup base.

99
00:04:56,320 --> 00:04:57,440
Will this work?

100
00:04:57,520 --> 00:04:59,160
That's not the soup base
of instant noodles.

101
00:04:59,720 --> 00:05:01,160
That's Sun Tou Tou's

102
00:05:01,480 --> 00:05:02,800
unique fever medicine.

103
00:05:03,520 --> 00:05:04,880
It just tastes similar.

104
00:05:05,720 --> 00:05:06,640
You see.

105
00:05:10,520 --> 00:05:11,360
She's sweating.

106
00:05:12,880 --> 00:05:15,080
This should be what the book
meant by "perspire".

107
00:05:16,320 --> 00:05:17,160
Tou Tou.

108
00:05:24,200 --> 00:05:25,360
I saw something just now.

109
00:05:26,320 --> 00:05:27,440
There's a scratch wound here.

110
00:05:27,440 --> 00:05:28,600
What's going on?

111
00:05:29,040 --> 00:05:30,000
I don't know.

112
00:05:30,480 --> 00:05:33,160
Ever since she was stung by
bugs in Hainan four months ago,

113
00:05:33,600 --> 00:05:34,920
she had rashes.

114
00:05:35,200 --> 00:05:36,320
The more she scratched it,
the bigger it grew.

115
00:05:36,720 --> 00:05:37,920
It's also filled with pus.

116
00:05:38,160 --> 00:05:39,680
Once a scab is formed,
it'll crack again.

117
00:05:39,920 --> 00:05:41,760
She suffered because of it.

118
00:05:42,600 --> 00:05:43,760
She's still like this

119
00:05:44,200 --> 00:05:45,200
even after applying all kinds
of ointments and medicine.

120
00:05:45,800 --> 00:05:47,640
If so, you can put this oil

121
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:49,240
in a bottle.

122
00:05:49,560 --> 00:05:50,400
You can rub it on her skin

123
00:05:50,400 --> 00:05:51,760
every day.

124
00:05:52,320 --> 00:05:54,040
It'll take around three to five days.

125
00:05:54,200 --> 00:05:56,520
She should recover as long as
she doesn't scratch them again.

126
00:05:56,520 --> 00:05:57,840
She won't be itchy after applying it.

127
00:05:57,840 --> 00:05:59,080
What kind of oil is this?

128
00:05:59,440 --> 00:06:01,040
-I'll leave it here.
-This is the egg...

129
00:06:05,200 --> 00:06:06,400
You don't even remember the name?

130
00:06:08,080 --> 00:06:10,240
This is Shendan Oil,

131
00:06:10,720 --> 00:06:11,600
which Master treasures a lot.

132
00:06:12,320 --> 00:06:13,720
What are you saying?

133
00:06:13,880 --> 00:06:14,720
You don't even remember the name.

134
00:06:14,720 --> 00:06:16,200
Shendan Oil is very precious.

135
00:06:16,640 --> 00:06:19,480
It doesn't contain any
chemicals or additives.

136
00:06:20,200 --> 00:06:22,120
It's child-friendly.

137
00:06:22,600 --> 00:06:23,440
And, it's very precious.

138
00:06:24,200 --> 00:06:25,080
It's used

139
00:06:25,080 --> 00:06:27,200
to treat all kinds of rashes.

140
00:06:28,040 --> 00:06:29,960
Judging from Tang Tang's condition,

141
00:06:30,480 --> 00:06:31,600
her fever should subside

142
00:06:31,960 --> 00:06:32,760
in half an hour.

143
00:06:32,920 --> 00:06:33,880
Don't be too worried.

144
00:06:34,480 --> 00:06:35,800
-Thank you.
-Don't mention it.

145
00:06:36,040 --> 00:06:37,440
If her fever doesn't subside
in half an hour,

146
00:06:37,720 --> 00:06:39,920
I'll look for your master.

147
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:40,960
That's impossible...

148
00:06:42,480 --> 00:06:43,360
Alright.

149
00:06:52,520 --> 00:06:54,560
You didn't utter a single word of truth.

150
00:06:54,760 --> 00:06:55,760
The ordinary egg yolk oil

151
00:06:55,760 --> 00:06:58,000
became Master's precious Shendan Oil
when you describe it.

152
00:07:00,760 --> 00:07:02,320
If she knows that the oil is cheap,

153
00:07:02,320 --> 00:07:03,240
easy to obtain,

154
00:07:03,360 --> 00:07:04,400
and made by me,

155
00:07:04,400 --> 00:07:05,600
do you think she'll use it?

156
00:07:06,880 --> 00:07:07,920
Look at how huge her house is.

157
00:07:09,040 --> 00:07:10,120
Will she believe me?

158
00:07:10,120 --> 00:07:11,040
Tell me.

159
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:17,040
You read Tang Tang's pulse, right?
How was it?

160
00:07:18,040 --> 00:07:19,200
She's fine. It's not a huge issue.

161
00:07:20,520 --> 00:07:21,320
Good.

162
00:07:21,320 --> 00:07:23,040
How did you know that
Tang Tang has eczema?

163
00:07:38,320 --> 00:07:39,320
I read her pulse.

164
00:07:40,200 --> 00:07:41,680
You're full of nonsense, aren't you?

165
00:07:42,080 --> 00:07:43,320
I'll call you Master if you can

166
00:07:43,320 --> 00:07:44,440
