198
00:08:54,320 --> 00:08:55,760
Make some porridge for her.

199
00:08:55,760 --> 00:08:56,760
Make it

200
00:08:56,960 --> 00:08:58,000
with rice bran oil.

201
00:08:58,200 --> 00:08:59,280
That can warm her stomach.

202
00:09:01,200 --> 00:09:02,160
Tou Tou,

203
00:09:03,080 --> 00:09:04,520
what medicine did you give
the child just now?

204
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:05,880
Hot pot soup.

205
00:09:07,640 --> 00:09:08,520
Hot pot soup?

206
00:09:09,200 --> 00:09:10,080
Good job.

207
00:09:10,400 --> 00:09:11,760
The successor of
the Jiang family's acupuncture sect

208
00:09:11,760 --> 00:09:12,760
is excellent indeed.

209
00:09:12,760 --> 00:09:13,680
She has mastered

210
00:09:13,680 --> 00:09:15,200
the Treatise On Febrile Diseases
Caused By Cold.

211
00:09:15,520 --> 00:09:16,440
Mr Zheng,

212
00:09:16,440 --> 00:09:17,440
you don't need to worry at all.

213
00:09:17,680 --> 00:09:18,880
With her skills,

214
00:09:19,120 --> 00:09:20,040
your daughter

215
00:09:20,520 --> 00:09:21,400
will be fine.

216
00:09:23,640 --> 00:09:24,600
You see,

217
00:09:26,080 --> 00:09:27,520
fever on children
usually lasts for one week.

218
00:09:27,720 --> 00:09:28,760
Usually,

219
00:09:28,760 --> 00:09:29,840
they'll perspire

220
00:09:30,120 --> 00:09:31,200
after taking fever medicine.

221
00:09:32,120 --> 00:09:33,200
Although it relieves her condition
on the surface,

222
00:09:33,640 --> 00:09:34,600
it also

223
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:36,080
affects her health.

224
00:09:36,320 --> 00:09:37,160
When her body is weak,

225
00:09:37,440 --> 00:09:39,320
pathogen will attack her body.

226
00:09:39,640 --> 00:09:40,560
After your daughter

227
00:09:40,760 --> 00:09:42,280
consumed the hot pot soup

228
00:09:42,520 --> 00:09:43,320
made by her,

229
00:09:44,000 --> 00:09:45,160
her body will grow strong.

230
00:09:45,960 --> 00:09:47,080
She'll be fine within a few days.

231
00:09:49,640 --> 00:09:50,480
Xin Zheng,

232
00:09:52,080 --> 00:09:53,560
you did great in teaching your student.

233
00:09:57,440 --> 00:09:58,280
Don't get too full of yourself.

234
00:09:58,280 --> 00:09:59,520
This is only your first patient.

235
00:09:59,680 --> 00:10:00,640
I'm not full at all.

236
00:10:01,560 --> 00:10:02,520
I just think

237
00:10:04,120 --> 00:10:05,200
that your father didn't deceive me.

238
00:10:05,400 --> 00:10:07,080
Saving real kids

239
00:10:07,080 --> 00:10:09,120
is much more fun than
playing with claw machines.

240
00:10:10,000 --> 00:10:10,880
There's a delicate feeling

241
00:10:11,320 --> 00:10:12,440
that I cannot describe.

242
00:10:16,200 --> 00:10:17,040
What do you think?

243
00:10:17,880 --> 00:10:18,800
You win again.

244
00:10:27,440 --> 00:10:29,400
Professor Ren, thank you so much.

245
00:10:29,880 --> 00:10:31,080
Your Shendan Oil

246
00:10:31,400 --> 00:10:32,520
worked miraculously.

247
00:10:33,520 --> 00:10:34,760
