250
00:10:38,360 --> 00:10:39,520
when we need it in the future?

251
00:10:43,440 --> 00:10:45,440
-Do you still feel itchy?
-No.

252
00:10:45,520 --> 00:10:46,520
You don't feel itchy now?

253
00:10:48,400 --> 00:10:49,960
Actually, this oil

254
00:10:51,200 --> 00:10:52,080
cannot be found anywhere.

255
00:10:52,400 --> 00:10:53,760
What about this?
I'll bring it for your child

256
00:10:53,960 --> 00:10:55,760
