if she needs it.

257
00:10:55,880 --> 00:10:57,080
Thank you in advance then.

258
00:10:57,080 --> 00:10:58,040
Don't mention it.

259
00:10:58,080 --> 00:10:59,400
Remember to rest well.

260
00:11:00,520 --> 00:11:02,000
-Goodbye.
-Say goodbye.

261
00:11:02,120 --> 00:11:03,040
Thank the miss

262
00:11:03,040 --> 00:11:04,200
and the mister.

263
00:11:13,320 --> 00:11:14,240
What?

264
00:11:14,880 --> 00:11:15,680
What oil did you give her?

265
00:11:16,520 --> 00:11:17,480
Egg yolk oil.

266
00:11:19,560 --> 00:11:21,040
