268
00:11:24,000 --> 00:11:26,760
Egg yolk oil is excellent
for itching skin, rashes

269
00:11:27,760 --> 00:11:29,000
with wound.

270
00:11:31,360 --> 00:11:32,520
You're promising indeed.

271
00:11:33,680 --> 00:11:34,760
We studied together.

272
00:11:34,760 --> 00:11:36,240
