alongside Warren Buffett?

569
00:23:01,840 --> 00:23:03,360
It's because he's rich.

570
00:23:04,760 --> 00:23:05,680
Being rich

571
00:23:05,880 --> 00:23:07,560
is the most obvious strength

572
