for all laymen to see.

573
00:23:09,840 --> 00:23:10,800
That's why

574
00:23:10,840 --> 00:23:12,240
ambitious youths chose

575
00:23:12,480 --> 00:23:13,640
to follow him.

576
00:23:14,360 --> 00:23:15,560
Does Warren Buffett love money?

577
00:23:15,760 --> 00:23:16,680
I don't think so.

578
00:23:17,080 --> 00:23:19,320
He bought his house for 50,000 dollars.

579
00:23:20,280 --> 00:23:21,880
