So, you see,

582
00:23:24,520 --> 00:23:27,240
Professor Ren, you can choose
to donate your money when you're rich.

583
00:23:28,280 --> 00:23:30,200
However, you mustn't stay poor.

584
00:23:30,920 --> 00:23:31,800
If you're poor,

585
00:23:31,920 --> 00:23:33,600
no one is willing to study under you.

586
00:23:35,280 --> 00:23:36,440
That makes total sense.

587
00:23:36,440 --> 00:23:38,440
You're the banner of the TCM industry.

588
00:23:38,760 --> 00:23:39,920
You're our symbol.

589
00:23:39,920 --> 00:23:40,800
With you around,

590
00:23:41,280 --> 00:23:42,280
the revival of the TCM industry

591
00:23:42,360 --> 00:23:43,760
is just around the corner.

592
00:23:45,640 --> 00:23:47,920
This is just the beginning.

593
00:23:48,320 --> 00:23:49,840
The TCM industrial park

594
00:23:49,840 --> 00:23:52,040
is just like a piece of land.

595
00:23:52,440 --> 00:23:53,360
The apprentice class

596
00:23:53,760 --> 00:23:55,280
is just like a seed.

597
00:23:55,760 --> 00:23:59,040
Professor Ren is the sun and rain.

598
00:23:59,800 --> 00:24:01,000
As for the rest,

599
00:24:01,200 --> 00:24:04,200
you guys are in charge of
watering and fertilizing the field.

600
00:24:04,440 --> 00:24:05,320
By then,

601
00:24:05,440 --> 00:24:06,280
when my tree

602
00:24:06,640 --> 00:24:09,080
is filled with fruits,

603
00:24:09,080 --> 00:24:11,440
we can share
the fruits of labour together.

604
00:24:14,160 --> 00:24:15,080
Good.

605
00:24:16,000 --> 00:24:17,680
Mr Liu, I agree with you.

606
00:24:18,760 --> 00:24:20,760
If so, let's pray that this seed of ours

607
00:24:21,120 --> 00:24:22,000
can grow into

608
00:24:22,200 --> 00:24:23,200
a huge tree.

609
00:24:23,520 --> 00:24:24,360
Here.

610
00:24:24,440 --> 00:24:25,760
Let's have a toast.

611
00:24:25,760 --> 00:24:26,640
Come.

612
00:24:27,360 --> 00:24:28,400
Come.

613
00:24:29,000 --> 00:24:30,320
Come. I'll replace liquor with tea.

614
00:24:30,360 --> 00:24:31,280
Come.

615
00:24:32,680 --> 00:24:33,560
What about this?

616
00:24:33,960 --> 00:24:34,880
Guys,

617
00:24:35,320 --> 00:24:37,600
I'm truly touched

618
00:24:38,520 --> 00:24:40,560
by your support for the TCM industry.

619
00:24:41,360 --> 00:24:43,040
Before I drink,

620
00:24:43,240 --> 00:24:44,880
I wish to express

621
00:24:44,880 --> 00:24:46,400
my stand clearly.

622
00:24:46,800 --> 00:24:48,160
This way, at least

623
00:24:48,400 --> 00:24:50,040
your excellent liquor won't go to waste.

624
00:24:52,120 --> 00:24:53,160
You see,

625
00:24:53,920 --> 00:24:55,040
I call a spade a spade.

626
00:24:55,160 --> 00:24:56,400
Warren Buffett is Warren Buffett.

627
00:24:56,400 --> 00:24:57,560
I am me.

628
00:24:58,560 --> 00:25:00,920
In the end,

629
00:25:02,080 --> 00:25:04,480
you and I aren't working for
our own sake.

630
00:25:04,520 --> 00:25:07,160
Let's not talk about
carrying forward the culture.

631
00:25:07,160 --> 00:25:08,880
That's just being boastful.

632
00:25:11,520 --> 00:25:13,440
First, we have to confirm

633
00:25:13,680 --> 00:25:15,320
the definition of wealth.

634
00:25:15,880 --> 00:25:17,040
So, what is wealth?

635
00:25:17,920 --> 00:25:19,040
Wealth doesn't mean

636
00:25:19,280 --> 00:25:21,040
the amount of money
you have in your bank account.

637
00:25:21,920 --> 00:25:23,560
If you don't spend that money

638
00:25:24,160 --> 00:25:26,160
on somewhere useful,

639
00:25:26,160 --> 00:25:28,400
it'll be a waste.

640
00:25:34,440 --> 00:25:35,440
For example,

641
00:25:36,080 --> 00:25:38,520
if you buy a house of
1,000 square meters,

642
00:25:38,800 --> 00:25:40,320
that means you're the slave
of that house.

643
00:25:41,400 --> 00:25:43,560
If you buy a ten million yuan car,

644
00:25:44,280 --> 00:25:45,680
I don't think the insurance company

645
00:25:46,040 --> 00:25:48,280
will insure your car.

646
00:25:49,080 --> 00:25:50,840
So guys, what's the definition
of insurance?

647
00:25:52,880 --> 00:25:54,560
It's God.

648
00:25:56,440 --> 00:25:58,760
God has a ledger.

649
00:25:59,880 --> 00:26:01,680
If you're on the righteous path,

650
00:26:02,800 --> 00:26:04,880
you can just give it your all
without any hesitations.

651
00:26:05,080 --> 00:26:06,640
However, if you're not,

652
00:26:07,040 --> 00:26:08,560
God will see everything.

653
00:26:10,760 --> 00:26:12,160
God can tell.

654
00:26:14,160 --> 00:26:15,280
You're being petty,

655
00:26:15,920 --> 00:26:16,760
you have ulterior motives, and so on.

656
00:26:22,760 --> 00:26:24,040
Therefore, being a doctor

657
00:26:24,040 --> 00:26:25,640
is different from other occupations.

658
00:26:26,400 --> 00:26:27,560
If doctors

659
00:26:28,160 --> 00:26:29,920
want to strike it rich,

660
00:26:31,920 --> 00:26:33,200
God will punish us.

661
00:26:35,080 --> 00:26:36,800
Let's just take

662
00:26:36,800 --> 00:26:39,320
my apprentice class as an example.

663
00:26:39,320 --> 00:26:40,680
Maybe the apprentice class

664
00:26:40,680 --> 00:26:42,640
might be a long

665
00:26:43,040 --> 00:26:44,320
and fruitless process.

666
00:26:45,400 --> 00:26:46,840
Maybe it'll bear fruit.

667
00:26:48,400 --> 00:26:49,640
That means

668
00:26:50,200 --> 00:26:52,080
we might not be able to witness
the result in our lifetime.

669
00:26:55,280 --> 00:26:56,240
I'm sure you guys know this too.

670
00:26:57,640 --> 00:26:58,760
It takes ten years to nurture a tree,

671
00:26:59,280 --> 00:27:00,320
but a hundred years to train a man.

672
00:27:00,320 --> 00:27:02,200
If you all wish

673
00:27:02,200 --> 00:27:04,440
to gain something from this,

674
00:27:04,880 --> 00:27:07,400
you shouldn't use the name of TCM.

675
00:27:08,000 --> 00:27:09,320
I'm not smart.

676
00:27:10,040 --> 00:27:11,440
But I'm not silly either.

677
00:27:12,160 --> 00:27:14,640
Mr Liu, in the future,

678
00:27:14,640 --> 00:27:17,000
you shouldn't hold gatherings like this.

679
00:27:17,560 --> 00:27:18,800
It's not worth it

680
00:27:19,640 --> 00:27:21,280
to spend your money on someone like me.

681
00:27:22,040 --> 00:27:22,880
It's not worth it.

682
00:27:26,520 --> 00:27:27,440
Here, let's have a toast.

683
00:27:33,920 --> 00:27:34,800
Excellent liquor.

684
00:28:01,920 --> 00:28:03,000
You scared me.

685
00:28:03,000 --> 00:28:04,280
I thought your father was here.

686
00:28:04,920 --> 00:28:06,400
Aren't you going to hand in
your homework tomorrow?

687
00:28:09,400 --> 00:28:10,360
I have so much work to complete.

688
00:28:11,040 --> 00:28:11,920
I gave it some thought.

689
00:28:12,200 --> 00:28:13,280
I can't finish copying them anyway.

690
00:28:13,680 --> 00:28:15,040
It's better to let your father
punish me.

691
00:28:15,280 --> 00:28:16,720
This way, it's satisfying
for both him and me.

692
00:28:17,280 --> 00:28:18,560
My father never punishes people.

693
00:28:21,040 --> 00:28:21,880
Is that so?

694
00:28:22,560 --> 00:28:24,360
He'll chase you out directly.

695
00:28:30,280 --> 00:28:31,760
This is no fun.

696
00:28:32,360 --> 00:28:34,280
He chases people out?

697
00:28:36,800 --> 00:28:37,800
How could I finish

698
00:28:38,800 --> 00:28:40,600
copying all of them?

699
00:28:41,280 --> 00:28:42,080
Look at them.

700
00:28:43,440 --> 00:28:44,280
Give it to me.

701
00:28:45,560 --> 00:28:46,840
-What are you doing?
-Make way.

702
00:28:47,080 --> 00:28:47,920
Wait.

703
00:28:49,400 --> 00:28:51,000
Grandson, what are you doing?

704
00:29:00,920 --> 00:29:02,560
Could it be that
you're trying to help me?

705
00:29:03,160 --> 00:29:04,080
To be honest,

706
00:29:05,440 --> 00:29:07,000
it's pretty difficult to imitate

707
00:29:07,680 --> 00:29:08,640
your terrible writing.

708
00:29:16,800 --> 00:29:17,640
I've left some space for you.

709
00:29:17,640 --> 00:29:18,560
Just fill in the blanks.

710
00:29:18,680 --> 00:29:19,560
Understood.

711
00:29:23,560 --> 00:29:24,720
Ling Ju?

712
00:29:30,400 --> 00:29:31,280
You're using your left hand?

713
00:29:31,560 --> 00:29:32,520
Are you sure you can do it?

714
00:29:32,640 --> 00:29:33,520
My left hand is better than your right.

715
00:29:36,400 --> 00:29:37,480
Why don't you use your foot then?

716
00:29:39,080 --> 00:29:40,760
Use your toes

717
00:29:40,760 --> 00:29:42,040
