718
00:29:42,040 --> 00:29:43,600
Grab it and write it like this.

719
00:29:44,320 --> 00:29:45,200
Can you do it?

720
00:29:46,440 --> 00:29:47,640
Can you write it backhand?

721
00:29:47,880 --> 00:29:48,920
Like this.

