00:29:49,160 --> 00:29:50,120
Like this.

723
00:29:50,160 --> 00:29:50,960
Like this.

724
00:29:52,160 --> 00:29:53,000
Like this.

725
00:29:56,080 --> 00:29:57,000
What about this?

726
00:29:58,000 --> 00:29:58,920
What about this?

727
00:29:59,640 --> 00:30:00,440
Put your arm at the back.

728
00:30:01,040 --> 00:30:02,560
This is pretty cool.

729
00:30:02,560 --> 00:30:03,800
What about this? Try and lift your leg.

730
00:30:05,040 --> 00:30:05,880
Can you do it like this?

731
00:30:16,400 --> 00:30:17,240
Grandson.

732
00:30:17,960 --> 00:30:18,880
I recognise

733
00:30:19,160 --> 00:30:20,160
all these characters.

734
00:30:20,240 --> 00:30:21,840
But I just don't understand them.

735
00:30:22,200 --> 00:30:24,200
What's the use of
writing and memorizing them

736
00:30:24,200 --> 00:30:25,280
every day?

737
00:30:26,800 --> 00:30:28,680
It'll be useful eventually.

738
00:30:28,960 --> 00:30:30,600
It's an enlightening process.

739
00:30:31,440 --> 00:30:33,520
Maybe you'll be enlightened one day.

740
00:30:33,920 --> 00:30:35,400
You recited it every day since young.

741
00:30:35,680 --> 00:30:36,680
Were you enlightened?

742
00:30:42,240 --> 00:30:43,120
Were you?

743
00:30:45,880 --> 00:30:47,040
Hey, were you enlightened?

744
00:30:47,040 --> 00:30:48,360
Is that so hard to answer?

745
00:30:50,160 --> 00:30:51,120
Enlightened...

746
00:30:51,800 --> 00:30:53,520
Were you enlightened?

747
00:30:53,520 --> 00:30:54,440
What do you mean?

748
00:30:57,400 --> 00:31:01,040
♫ Waves upon waves ♫

