00:31:05,760 --> 00:31:07,280
Nephew, you're back.

751
00:31:08,040 --> 00:31:08,920
You're still awake at this hour?

752
00:31:08,920 --> 00:31:09,720
What were you up to?

753
00:31:09,920 --> 00:31:12,120
I was practising my Cantonese.

754
00:31:13,800 --> 00:31:14,600
What's the matter?

755
00:31:15,280 --> 00:31:16,120
What are you doing?

756
00:31:18,560 --> 00:31:19,920
Didn't you tell me to copy it?

757
00:31:24,760 --> 00:31:25,640
I'll check it tomorrow.

758
00:31:26,480 --> 00:31:27,360
Fine with me.

