00:31:28,160 --> 00:31:29,320
Don't try to trick me.

760
00:31:29,440 --> 00:31:30,600
Got it.

761
00:31:53,520 --> 00:31:54,400
You're back.

762
00:31:57,320 --> 00:31:58,960
Did you take alcohol?

763
00:31:59,800 --> 00:32:00,640
Only a little.

764
00:32:01,800 --> 00:32:03,160
I drank one cup
and severed my ties with them.

765
00:32:03,800 --> 00:32:04,920
The liquor was excellent.

766
00:32:05,800 --> 00:32:06,680
What a waste of fine liquor.

767
00:32:07,680 --> 00:32:08,960
Who did you offend again?

768
00:32:10,280 --> 00:32:11,120
Wait.

769
00:32:11,280 --> 00:32:12,800
Who offended you again?

770
00:32:12,800 --> 00:32:14,280
"Offend" isn't the right term for it.

771
00:32:15,080 --> 00:32:16,000
It's called

772
