773
00:32:22,680 --> 00:32:24,560
I guess we're fated to part ways then.

774
00:32:30,280 --> 00:32:31,240
I'm getting old.

775
00:32:31,800 --> 00:32:33,080
I got drunk after drinking one cup.

776
00:32:33,320 --> 00:32:34,440
I was spouting nonsense.

777
00:32:37,800 --> 00:32:39,480
Did you see Tou Tou
when you came upstairs?

778
00:32:39,920 --> 00:32:40,840
She's doing her homework.

779
00:32:44,680 --> 00:32:45,680
She's not doing it.

780
00:32:45,680 --> 00:32:47,200
Your son's doing it for her.

781
00:32:48,040 --> 00:32:50,280
No wonder the room
next to ours is so quiet.

782
00:32:52,280 --> 00:32:54,400
Tian Zhen never treated her
as an equal before.

783
00:32:54,800 --> 00:32:57,080
Why is he trying to do
her homework for her now?

784
00:32:57,680 --> 00:33:00,080
Your son is just trying
to atone for his mistakes.

785
00:33:02,440 --> 00:33:04,360
However, he's still a good boy.

786
00:33:04,680 --> 00:33:05,800
At least he knows his faults now.

787
00:33:09,800 --> 00:33:12,240
I guess the phrase
"In wine, there is truth" is true.

788
00:33:14,920 --> 00:33:16,520
You should drink more in the future.

789
00:33:25,080 --> 00:33:27,600
Don't tell me you're going
to check it page by page?

790
00:33:35,520 --> 00:33:36,400
Alright.

791
00:33:37,120 --> 00:33:38,400
You're done with this month's task.

792
00:33:39,640 --> 00:33:40,520
The drinking incident

793
00:33:41,040 --> 00:33:41,960
is over now.

794
00:33:43,320 --> 00:33:44,680
It was an accident.

795
00:33:44,680 --> 00:33:46,240
I will never get drunk again.

796
00:33:46,240 --> 00:33:47,760
I'm serious. I can hold my liquor well.

797
00:33:48,360 --> 00:33:49,280
Alright.

798
00:33:49,320 --> 00:33:50,120
You can proceed with it in the future.

799
00:33:51,360 --> 00:33:52,440
You mean taking alcohol?

800
00:33:53,800 --> 00:33:54,760
Writing.

801
00:33:56,000 --> 00:33:57,640
What do you mean?

802
00:34:00,440 --> 00:34:01,480
But why?

803
00:34:01,480 --> 00:34:03,000
I thought you said
the incident was over?

804
00:34:03,000 --> 00:34:04,120
Why do I still have to write?

805
00:34:05,680 --> 00:34:07,120
This is your punishment.

806
00:34:07,360 --> 00:34:08,520
After this, you'll be doing homework.

807
00:34:11,200 --> 00:34:13,080
I can memorise them.

808
00:34:13,200 --> 00:34:14,120
I can memorise their
medicinal properties,

809
00:34:14,120 --> 00:34:15,000
the Pharmacopoeia, and everything else.

810
00:34:15,160 --> 00:34:16,040
Can I not write them down?

811
00:34:16,040 --> 00:34:17,600
Why must I write them down?

812
00:34:17,600 --> 00:34:19,080
Why do you have so many questions?

813
00:34:19,880 --> 00:34:20,960
Just write when I tell you to.

814
00:34:21,680 --> 00:34:23,000
You'll understand why eventually.

815
00:34:23,600 --> 00:34:25,320
I'm not willing to do it
without knowing what's going on.

816
00:34:25,320 --> 00:34:26,120
That's just

817
00:34:26,120 --> 00:34:27,840
a waste of time.

818
00:34:28,280 --> 00:34:29,200
And,

819
00:34:30,000 --> 00:34:31,280
you're not telling me

820
00:34:32,800 --> 00:34:33,640
because you have no idea too.

821
00:34:34,280 --> 00:34:35,120
Was it because

822
00:34:36,360 --> 00:34:37,840
your master taught you
in the same manner?

823
00:34:38,280 --> 00:34:39,800
Is that why you copy him blindly

824
00:34:39,800 --> 00:34:40,680
and teach me in the same way?

825
00:34:41,120 --> 00:34:43,440
Is this your so-called legacy?

826
00:34:44,000 --> 00:34:44,840
And, do you think

827
00:34:44,920 --> 00:34:46,920
